metadata.name: Departure
metadata.description:
I don't just drop it. I launch it like a rocket outward into space, my final frontier. I send a probe with every piece to take me where no one has gone before. Every experience is a new exploration, a new life. To seek out me in a universe that is me. When I reach my destination, I have one hell of a story to tell.

Created with Cinema 4D, Octane Render, and After Effects / March 2021
